      *****************************************************************
     C     *INZSR        BEGSR
 
     C     *ENTRY        PLIST
      *
      * INPUTS
      *
      ** Return Code
     C                   PARM                    RetCodeIn
      *
      ** Other parms
      *
      ** Field(s) requiring validation
     C                   PARM                    DDCLSM            6
      *
      *
      * OUTPUTS
      *
      *
      * Error fields/message IDs/message data (arrays) from/to caller
     C                   PARM                    FldNamXAr
     C                   PARM                    MsgIDXAr
     C                   PARM                    MsgDtaXAr
      ** CLS Settlement Member      - OK
     C                   PARM                    DDCLSMOK          1
